## üìå Tips for a Great Cybersecurity Portfolio Website

**Content to include:**
‚úî Personal bio & professional summary
‚úî Technical skills (tools, languages, platforms)
‚úî Detailed *project case studies* (problem ‚Üí approach ‚Üí results)
‚úî Certifications & training badges
‚úî Links to *GitHub repos*, capture-the-flag write-ups, labs
‚úî Contact info + LinkedIn/GitHub links

**Structure ideas:**
üìå One-page portfolio
üìå Multi-section site with Projects | Skills | Blog | Contact
üìå GitHub Pages version with markdown and project links

---

## üß∞ Where to Host Your Portfolio

* **GitHub Pages** ‚Äì free hosting with custom domain support
* **Netlify / Vercel** ‚Äì free HTTPS hosting for static sites
* **Neocities / Static hosts** ‚Äì for simple HTML + CSS pages

